flowchart TD
    A[IngestDocument\nHTTP trigger] --> B[DocumentProcessOrchestrator (Durable)]
    B --> C[ClasificarActivity]
    C --> D1[Azure Document Intelligence]
    C --> D2[GPT 4o-mini\n(fallback si DI < umbralFallback)]
    D1 --> E1[ConfianzaDI]
    D2 --> E2[ConfianzaGPT]
    E1 & E2 --> F[ConfigurableClasificarDataProvider\npropaga Confianza + ProveedorClasif]
    F --> G[ExtraerActivity]
    G --> H1[Azure Content Understanding\n(ExtracCU)]
    G --> H2[GPT 4o-mini\n(fallback)]
    H1 --> I1[ConfianzaExtraccion]
    H2 --> I2[confianza_extraccion (self-report)]
    I1 & I2 --> J[ValidarActivity]
    J --> K[Motor de reglas\nConfianzaValidacion = 1 - errores/reglas_req]
    K --> L[ConfidenceCalculator.Global\nMIN(clasif, extrac?, valid)]
    L --> M[ConfidenceCalculator.EstadoCalidad\numbralOK=0.85, umbralRevision=0.70]
    M --> N{ConfianzaGlobal >= 0.85}
    N -->|Sí| O[OK]
    N -->|No| P{ConfianzaGlobal >= 0.70}
    P -->|Sí| Q[REVISION]
    P -->|No| R[ERROR]
